

# Commit Format:
# <type>(<scope>): <summary>
#
# Recommended types:
#   feat     – a new feature
#   fix      – a bug fix
#   docs     – documentation only
#   style    – formatting, missing semicolons, etc.
#   refactor – code change that isn't a fix or feat
#   perf     – performance improvement
#   test     – adding or refactoring tests
#   chore    – build, CI, config, etc.
#
# Example:
# feat(crm): add summer activities dropdown to profile page